{"tid":2233487,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區內零售舖吹冷風 空置率13%新高","createTime":"2020-10-07T07:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T07:15:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"39e774e5cb01246a994c0f4974e65378f36367a2","tid":2233487,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/BPCWRERGXBD33P6MWJKIJRYJEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FBPCWRERGXBD33P6MWJKIJRYJEI%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmdjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=1b60a512\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FBPCWRERGXBD33P6MWJKIJRYJEI%2F&h=f6a4635f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/BPCWRERGXBD33P6MWJKIJRYJEI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n區內零售舖吹冷風 空置率13%新高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Itv2Hbf7xS5Yrv260BJHq7KYIf0=/1280x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QDGIMOVBVRBRTHXNXWVION35ZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FItv2Hbf7xS5Yrv260BJHq7KYIf0%3D%2F1280x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQDGIMOVBVRBRTHXNXWVION35ZI.jpg&h=35cb11d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■銅鑼灣區商舖空置率錄得13.2%，再創新高。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港第三波疫情漸趨緩和，惟經濟復蘇需時，商舖物業價格偏軟。戴德梁行最新發表本港第三季寫字樓及零售租賃報告指，核心區商舖租金期內跌幅收窄，惟各區空置率仍持續攀升，其中銅鑼灣區空置率新近錄得13.2%，再創新高。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：銅鑼灣樓上舖慘蝕3,200萬  「物流張」見紅 6年貶值44%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年商廈租金料跌21%<br />\n<br />\n戴德梁行報告指出，第三季商舖租金跌幅情況改善，惟核心區租金跌幅依然高踞各區，銅鑼灣及中環舖租分別按季跌7.9%和7.8%。不過，零售市況反彈乏力，各區相關空置率均升至雙位數，其中以銅鑼灣為重災區，空置率由上季7.9%升至13.2%，屬歷史新高。戴德梁行香港商舖部主管林應威表示，疫情影響已反映在現有租金跌幅上，而大部份業主未有意欲再大幅劈價招租，相信核心區租金將不會有更大跌幅，並預料零售市道最快明年第二季方有望復蘇。<br />\n<br />\n商廈方面，上述報告亦指，。。。。。。。"}]}